ic_en","text":"and its being apart from the side;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatolN","text_ar":"فَتْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M: [thus in the TT as from the M; being there written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fatoal","text_ar":"فَتَْل"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) this [or rather the like of this] in the shank and foot of the camel is a fault. (M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","TA","M","K"]}]}}